lgia. Dial up the cushioning and stay injury free.\n      </p>\n\n      <div class=\"ORTHOPLP-icons\">\n        <div class=\"ORTHOPLP-icons-container\">\n          <div class=\"ORTHOPLP-icon\">\n            <img alt=\"Aetrex Alignment\" src=\"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0860/3634/9241/files/11_05_Alignment_Icon_3953a3b4-a2c0-4f20-9606-e698f502e6e8.png?v=1743510968\" title=\"Aetrex Alignment\" />\n            <p>Alignment</p>\n          </div>\n          <div class=\"ORTHOPLP-icon\">\n            <img alt=\"Aetrex Arch Support\" src=\"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0860/3634/9241/files/11_05_ArchSupport_Icon_16a878f3-907c-4da1-a1b9-dcd84e7f430c.png?v=1743510968\" title=\"Aetrex Arch Support\" />\n            <p>Arch Support</p>\n          </div>\n          <div class=\"ORTHOPLP-icon\">\n            <img alt=\"Aetrex Superior Cushioning\" src=\"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0860/3634/9241/files/11_05_ExoFoamComfort_Icon_c8e0c521-3b4b-4e21-8bc1-a78c4e38e0db.png?v=1743510968\" title=\"Aetrex Superior Cushioning\" />\n            <p>Superior Cushioning</p>\n          </div>\n          <div class=\"ORTHOPLP-icon\">\n            <img alt=\"Aetrex Pain Relief\" src=\"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0860/3634/9241/files/11_05_PainRelief_Icon_826e8ac9-4782-4038-bbc2-7f0cc21e23a1.png?v=1743510968\" title=\"Aetrex Pain Relief\" />\n            <p>Pain Relief</p>\n          </div>\n        </div>\n      </div>\n    </div>\n\n    <div class=\"ORTHOPLP-image-box\">\n      <img src=\"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0860/3634/9241/files/walking_rev02.jpg?v=1743507243\" alt=\"Walking background image\" />\n    </div>\n  </div>\n</div>",
